                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Post grades online, with a tool like Schoology, or in a non-editable Google Sheet. Kids can see grades and complete makeup assignments.
                        This (can potentially) end fights around submitting work, printing makeup work, etc.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Handle individual situations as they arise. If a small group of kids can't handle computers, don't block the whole class from using computers.
